<Container: 71d426cad9d3> with image postgres:16-alpine to be ready ...\r\nINFO     testcontainers.core.container:container.py:98 Pulling image redis:7-alpine\r\nINFO     testcontainers.core.container:container.py:125 Container started: 290a46ef1acd\r\nINFO     testcontainers.core.waiting_utils:waiting_utils.py:52 Waiting for container <Container: 290a46ef1acd> with image redis:7-alpine to be ready ...\r\nINFO     testcontainers.core.waiting_utils:waiting_utils.py:52 Waiting for container <Container: 290a46ef1acd> with image redis:7-alpine to be ready ...\r\nINFO     testcontainers.core.waiting_utils:waiting_utils.py:52 Waiting for container <Container: 290a46ef1acd> with image redis:7-alpine to be ready ...\r\n============================== warnings summary ===============================\r\ntests/integration/test_usage_export_perf.py::test_export_p95_timing_sanity_at_the_row_cap\r\n  C:\\Users\\brett\\OneDrive\\Documents\\GitHub\\meterly-pipeline-test\\src\\main.py:21: StarletteDeprecationWarning: 'HTTP_413_REQUEST_ENTITY_TOO_LARGE' is deprecated. Use 'HTTP_413_CONTENT_TOO_LARGE' instead.\r\n    from src.api.errors import register_error_handlers\r\n\r\ntests/integration/test_usage_export_perf.py::test_export_p95_timing_sanity_at_the_row_cap\r\n  C:\\Users\\brett\\OneDrive\\Documents\\GitHub\\meterly-pipeline-test\\src\\main.py:21: StarletteDeprecationWarning: 'HTTP_422_UNPROCESSABLE_ENTITY' is deprecated. Use 'HTTP_422_UNPROCESSABLE_CONTENT' instead.\r\n    from src.api.errors import register_error_handlers\r\n\r\n-- Docs: https://docs.pytest.org/en/stable/how-to/capture-warnings.html\r\n=========================== short test summary info ===========================\r\nFAILED tests/integration/test_usage_export_perf.py::test_export_p95_timing_sanity_at_the_row_cap\r\n1 failed, 2 warnings in 40.39s","is_error":false}]},"uuid":"821cbc2b-00f3-45df-88ee-4acc5c73f53b","timestamp":"2026-07-09T18:34:25.943Z","sourceToolAssistantUUID":"f966babc-dc48-4b00-a431-5596fe934734